fields.name: Jam
fields.description: Alternating plum purple amethyst roses and voluminous freshwater pearls marry each other in this delectable berry necklace, reminiscent of sticky fingers and cut off crusts. Dance your way into everyone’s hearts with this sugary sweet treat.

fields.name: Single Strand
fields.description: This simple, yet sophisticated necklace has been styled by Bella Hadid many times. The creme-colored pearls accentuate our bedazzled logo pendant. Strung by hand with the purest silk.

fields.name: Mermaid
fields.description: You ever know what lies beneath the surface... Dive deeper and you'll be amazed to discover a magnetic mermaid cloaked in sea-salty kelp. She may be shy at first... but offer her a shimmering conch shell and she will adorn you with all the ocean’s most dazzling jewels.

fields.name: Blue Sky
fields.description: It’s blue skies from here on out with this peaceful pearly necklace. Consisting of beaming blue agate and freshwater pearls, this cloud-inspired piece is ideal for day dreaming and field frolicking. Feel the cool breeze of a warm summer's day as you adorn your neck with this slice of paradise.
